@themeId = INSERT_THEME_ID_HERE
@templateId = INSERT_TEMPLATE_ID_HERE

### Portfolio komplett abrufen (inkl. Projekte, Skills, Links, Experience, Education, Themes)
GET {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/full
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Alle Templates abrufen
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates

### Einzelnes Template abrufen
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates/{{templateId}}

### Uebersetzungen im Portfolio auflisten
GET {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/translations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Uebersetzung erstellen
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/translations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "languageCode": "en",
    "title": "My Portfolio",
    "description": "English translation"
}

### Uebersetzung aktualisieren
PUT {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/translations/{{translationId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "title": "My Updated Portfolio",
    "description": "Updated English translation"
}

### Uebersetzung loeschen
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/translations/{{translationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Versionen im Portfolio auflisten
GET {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Version aus aktuellem Portfoliozustand erstellen
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Einzelne Version abrufen
GET {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/versions/{{versionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Version aktivieren
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/versions/{{versionId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Version loeschen
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/versions/{{versionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Projekte im Portfolio auflisten
GET {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Projekt erstellen
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "title": "Backend API Projekt",
    "description": "REST-API mit Node.js und MSSQL",
    "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/project-api.png",
    "projectUrl": "https://example.com/project/backend-api",
    "githubUrl": "https://github.com/example/backend-api",
    "startDate": "2024-01-01",
    "endDate": "2024-06-01"
}

### Projekt aktualisieren
PUT {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "title": "Backend API Projekt v2",
    "description": "Aktualisierte Beschreibung",
    "githubUrl": "https://github.com/example/backend-api-v2"
}

### Projektbild hochladen (multipart/form-data)
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/projects/{{projectId}}/image
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="projektbild.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./projektbild.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### Projekt loeschen
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

